carbonenginejs/reader-dxbc
==========================

A pure-JavaScript reader for Microsoft DXBC (Direct3D compiled shader
bytecode) containers and the SM4/SM5 instruction token stream.

Contains no Microsoft code. The token-stream layout follows Microsoft's
public d3d11TokenizedProgramFormat documentation. Unity Technologies'
HLSLcc (MIT) was used as a behavioral reference while auditing instruction
semantics; no HLSLcc source is included in this repository.

